text: Harold V. Dutton Jr. is a Democratic member of the Texas House of Representatives representing District 142. He was first elected in 1984 and is one of the longest-serving members of the Texas House of Representatives. ==References== ==External links== *Legislative page * Harold Dutton Jr. at the Texas Tribune Category:Living people Category:Members of the Texas House of Representatives Category:Texas Southern University alumni Category:21st- century American politicians Category:Texas Democrats Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
